  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/b9e1a7a99ec7d24ca69ca0e3dc283968.avif?t=1752174974\" width=480 height=155 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You have one goal: ANNIHILATE AS MANY WAVES AS YOU CAN!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the pilot of the <strong>SANDRIPPER</strong>, a <strong>dual-wielding hover tank.</strong> Push your<strong> nuclear engine</strong> to its melting point as you <strong>rip</strong> through wave after wave of a ruthless planetary invasion force. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/00aa84f47f51792dab0afa124c803cab.poster.avif?t=1752174974\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/00aa84f47f51792dab0afa124c803cab.webm?t=1752174974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/00aa84f47f51792dab0afa124c803cab.mp4?t=1752174974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPERIMENTAL FUN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dual-wield the 9 <strong>MULTI-FUNCTION</strong> weapons along with their strange variants to create the ultimate annihilation machine. Randomized waves, upgrades, and a  destructible map create endless chaos to take advantage of. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even your <strong>ENGINE</strong> is a weapon!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/1671dcca46a77d8cf7056b05c218a37a.poster.avif?t=1752174974\" width=544 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/1671dcca46a77d8cf7056b05c218a37a.webm?t=1752174974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/1671dcca46a77d8cf7056b05c218a37a.mp4?t=1752174974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TWO DIFFERENT GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ENDLESS MODE: </strong> Find new weapons, upgrade your Sandripper, and dominate each increasingly difficult wave. Each day also has a new <strong>online leaderboard</strong>, and a new chance beat your friends!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SEEDED CHALLENGE MODE:</strong> If you don't fancy randomness, every few days a new pre-generated run is created for all players to experience and master. An insane predetermined sequence of events with its own leaderboard to climb!    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/287697c7c52f4872e5eeaf1c24a8a658.poster.avif?t=1752174974\" width=600 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/287697c7c52f4872e5eeaf1c24a8a658.webm?t=1752174974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/287697c7c52f4872e5eeaf1c24a8a658.mp4?t=1752174974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRY, DIE, REPEAT.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hone your skills, unlock weapons, and discover new strategies with each sub-20 minute long attempt. Gradually increasing your skill until you become a <strong>master of OBLITERATION</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/038da3c20b62ce7a1c5c4ffa1c4e858e.avif?t=1752174974\" width=447 height=180 /></span></p>",
